    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
        <span aria-hidden="true">Ã—</span>
    </button>
    <h2><i class="fa fa-bell" aria-hidden="true"></i> COVID-19 Update</h2>
    <p>Yale Library is open to faculty, students, and staff approved to be on campus. More info at <a href="https://web.library.yale.edu/news/2020/03/updates-covid-19-yale-library-online">COVID-19 updates</a>.</p>
